### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "isbn": "9780140449136",
  "title": "Meditations",
  "authors": ["Marcus Aurelius"],
  "description": "Classic Stoic philosophy.",
  "thumbnail": "https://example.com/meditations.jpg",
  "status": "DESEADO",
  "rating": 5
}

### List all books for current user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Find one book by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Search books by query
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/search?q=meditations
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Update book status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/books/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "status": "LEYENDO"
}
